---
title: BBQ Ranch Chicken Flatbreads Lightning Prep
description: In our humble opinion, flatbreads > pizza, any day! We know that may sound blasphemous, but stick with us. First of all, the golden, crispy crust is a veritable blank canvas. It’s not beholden to simply marinara and mozz! In fact, ours got a little wacky (in the best way possible): topped with tangy-sweet BBQ chicken, mozzarella, white cheddar, and a drizzle of ranch dressing. Basically, everything you want to eat. Can your ’za do that?! Yeah, we didn’t think so.
